WEBVTT

00:00:09.579 --> 00:00:12.204
Bilasizmi? Bizni Yerning boshqa 
qismidagi hayot bilan

00:00:12.371 --> 00:00:14.454
juda kam narsa jaratib turadi.

00:00:14.663 --> 00:00:20.538
O’ylaymanki, bularning asosida bizning 
bitmas-tuganmas xayolot kuchimiz yotadi.

00:00:23.746 --> 00:00:27.454
Xayolot bu yo’q narsalarni 
eslash qobiliyatidir.

00:00:29.413 --> 00:00:31.621
Tasavvur qilish orqali
kelajakni ko’rish,